}

\caption{\label{fig-alignment_heatmap}Heatmap showing the correspondence
between the seven identified food-web modules (rows) and the principal
components (columns) capturing 80\% of cumulative variance. High values
(darker shading) indicate strong alignment, where a specific module's
internal structure drives the variation captured by that PC. Both rows
and columns are hierarchically clustered to highlight similarities in
how different structural dimensions contribute to the overall food-web
architecture.}

\end{figure}
